khaleja ( also known as mahesh khaleja ) is a 2010 indian telugu-language fantasy-action comedy film starring mahesh babu and anushka shetty and directed by trivikram srinivas .   it is the second collaboration between mahesh babu and trivikram after athadu .   singanamala ramesh and c kalyan produced the film as a kanaka ratna movies production .   mahesh babu plays the role of a cab driver in the film , while prakash raj plays the lead antagonist .   the film is based on illegal-mining in india , and related environmental damage .   the film marks mahesh babu 's return as an actor after a three year hiatus .   sunil , ali and brahmanandam play key comedy roles .   the film was released on 7 october 2010 .   the film won two filmfare south awards for best male playback singer and best lyricist .   the film was dubbed into tamil as bhadra / bhiramma buthiran , in hindi as jigar kaleja , bengali as ekai eksho and in oriya as abatar .   it was declared as a hit at the box office .